NOTE: В основном тут меняются указатели в двунаправленных списках позиции.
 NOTE: У текущей позиции. У соседних позиций владельца. У соседних позиций нового владельца.
 NOTE: Первая и последняя позиция и кол-во позиций у старого и нового владельцев.
 NOTE: Меняется owner и (handler -> owner).
 NOTE: Изменение ownerWhitelist не требуется, доступ отключится из-за смены владельца позиции.

adjustPosition(uint256,int256,int256,byt.details: Adjust the position keeping the generated stablecoin or collateral freed in the positionHandler address.

params._positionId: The position id to be adjusted

allowManagePosition(uint256,address,uint.details: Allow/disallow a user to manage the position

params._ok: Ok flag to allow/disallow. 1 for allow and 0 for disallow.
params._user: The address to be allowed for managing the position

params._user: The address of user that will be allowed to do such an action to msg.sender

exportPosition(uint256,address).details: Export the positions's lockedCollateral and debtShare to a different destination address The destination address must allow position's owner to do so.

params._destination: The PositionHandler to be exported to
params._positionId: The position id to be exported

give(uint256,address).details: Give the position ownership to a destination address

params._destination: The destination to be a new owner of the position
params._positionId: The position id to be given away ownership

params._positionId: The position id to be moved to this PositionManager
params._source: The source PositionHandler to be moved to this PositionManager

params._positionId: The position id to move collateral from
params._wad: The amount in wad to be moved

movePosition(uint256,uint256).details: Move position's lockedCollateral and debtShare from the source PositionHandler to the destination PositionHandler

params._positionId: The position id to move stablecoin from
params._rad: The amount in rad to be moved

params._collateralPoolId: The collateral pool id that will be used for this position
params._user: The user address that is owned this position
